","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event31-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"就算外出也沒有什麼危險的怪物，可以接的任務，\n那個在遊戲裡面就像是工作一樣，\n都是些既簡單又安全的任務，不太玩遊戲的人也可以","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event31-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"開心地體驗NFO的世界，這座村莊就是被設計成這種構造，\n是個非常棒的地方唷( ‘ω’ )　其實這座村莊的\n村長丹凱因原本是這個世界上超有名的驍勇善戰的勇者","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event31-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"在他和怪物戰鬥時，大陸各處的人類之間\n也開始鬥爭，他被捲進去受了嚴重的傷，\n就無法再戰了(＝ω＝.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event31-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"RinRin","body":"即便如此他仍為了達成沒有怪物的和平世界，\n從這座小小的村莊將像我們這樣的幾千名幾萬名冒險者送出去，\n並在背後支援，啊，我們現在手上拿著在丹凱